name: The Titan Fist
description:
Second part of "Children of the Void" series. Sequel to "The Hungry Swarm [Wastelands]". A long time ago, a UED expedition has come to Koprulu sector. It was desintegrated. But there were several people who uncovered a horrible truth behind the UED and their attack on Koprulu... The map's using a unique trading system (at least i've written it on my own and never seen anything like this before).
Should be fun for BW fans - that's why it's called so. Currently EU only.
